Sentencas: A new blackbox technique has been presented in this article for model estimation of solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) for providing better results.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The proposed method is based on a hierarchical radial basis function (HRBF).
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The presented method is then developed by a new modified metaheuristic called developed coronavirus herd immunity algorithm (DCHIA).
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The suggested model has been named DCHIA-HRBF.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The proposed model is then trained by some data and prepared for identification and prediction.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The model is then analyzed and put in comparison with several latest techniques for validation of the efficiency of the technique.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is also verified by the empirical data to prove its validation with the real data.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results show that the best cost for the performance index which is the network error, is achieved by the proposed developed coronavirus herd immunity algorithm with about 119.442, which is satisfying for the considered function and target against the other state-of-the-art methods.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: As a result, the simulation results specified that the suggested DCHIA-HRBF delivers high effectiveness as an identifier and prediction tool for the SOFCs.
Titulo: Optimized hierarchical radial basis function neural networks by developing coronavirus herd immunity optimizer for solid oxide fuel cells
